{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height\"><code>height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/mozOpaque\"><code>mozOpaque</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width\"><code>width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>captureStream()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext\"><code>getContext()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/mozFetchAsStream\"><code>mozFetchAsStream()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toBlob\"><code>toBlob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toDataURL\"><code>toDataURL()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/transferControlToOffscreen\"><code>transferControlToOffscreen()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/webglcontextlost_event\"><code>webglcontextlost</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Das <strong><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></strong> interface bietet Eigenschaften und Methoden zum Manipulieren des Layouts und der Darstellung des <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code>-Elements. Das <code>HTMLCanvasElement</code> interface erbt außerdem Eigenschaften und Methoden des <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> interface.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Erbt Eigenschaften von seinem Elternelement, </em><em><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.height_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Ein positiver <code>integer</code>, der das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas#attr-height\"><code>height</code></a> HTML-Attribut des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> Elements in CSS-Pixeln repräsentiert. Wenn nicht definiert oder wenn es auf einen nicht erlaubten Wert (z.B. einen negativen Wert) gesetzt wird, wird der Standardwert <strong>150</strong> verwendet.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.mozopaque_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/mozOpaque\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.mozOpaque</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a>, der das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas#attr-moz-opaque\"><code>moz-opaque</code></a> HTML-Attribut des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> Elements repräsentiert. Es sagt dem canvas, ob auf Transparenz verzichtet werden soll. Falls <code>true</code>, kann das Zeichnen auf dem canvas beschleunigt werden.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.width_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Ein positiver <code>integer</code>, der das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas#attr-width\"><code>width</code></a> HTML-Attribut des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> Elements in CSS-Pixeln anzeigt. Wenn nicht definiert oder wenn es auf einen nicht erlaubten Wert (z.B. einen negativen Wert) gesetzt wird, wird der Standardwert <strong>300</strong> verwendet.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Erbt Eigenschaften von seinem Elternelement, </em><em><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.capturestream_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Gibt ein <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> zurück, dieses ist ein Echtzeit-Video der Oberfläche des canvas.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.getcontext_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Gibt einen context des canvas zurück oder <code>null</code>, falls die context-ID nicht unterstützt wird. Ein context ermöglicht es, auf dem canvas zu zeichnen. Der Aufruf dieser Methode mit <code>\"2d\"</code> gibt ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a> Objekt zurück, während er mit <code>\"experimental-webgl\"</code> oder <code>\"webgl\"</code> ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext</code></a> Objekt zurückgibt. Dieser context ist nur bei Browsern möglich, die <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">WebGL</a> unterstützen.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.todataurl\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toDataURL\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.toDataURL()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a data-URL containing a representation of the image in the format specified by the <code>type</code> parameter (defaults to <code>png</code>). The returned image is in a resolution of 96dpi.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.toblob_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toBlob\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.toBlob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Creates a <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> object representing the image contained in the canvas; this file may be cached on the disk or stored in memory at the discretion of the user agent.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.transfercontroltooffscreen_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/transferControlToOffscreen\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.transferControlToOffscreen()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Transfers control to an <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> object, either on the main thread or on a worker.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.mozgetasfile_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.mozGetAsFile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> object representing the image contained in the canvas; this file is a memory-based file, with the specified <code>name</code>. If <code>type</code> is not specified, the image type is <code>image/png</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-fromelement/#html-media-element-media-capture-extensions\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Media Capture from DOM Elements<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'HTMLCanvasElement' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Adds the method <code>captureStream()</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#the-canvas-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'HTMLCanvasElement' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>The method <code>getContext()</code> now returns a <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>RenderingContext</code></a> rather than an opaque <code>object</code>.<br>\n    The methods <code>probablySupportsContext()</code>, <code>setContext()</code> and <code>transferControlToProxy()</code>have been added.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/scripting-1.html#the-canvas-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'HTMLCanvasElement' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/scripting-1.html#the-canvas-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'HTMLCanvasElement' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompatibilität","title":"Browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support (<code>2D</code> context)</td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3.6\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2010-01-21.\">3.6</a> (1.9.2)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>9.0 [1]</td>\n   <td>3.1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>toBlob()</code></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span> (bug <a href=\"https://crbug.com/67587\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">67587</a>)</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/19\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2013-02-19.\">19</a> (19) [2]</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span> (bug <a href=\"https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=71270\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">71270</a>)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>probablySupportsContext()</code>,<br>\n    <code>setContext()</code>,<br>\n    <code>transferControlToProxy()</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</spa